{
  "stem": "20083.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But after a few minutes, you-- I got-- I wouldn't say I got used to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I quieted-- calmed down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, OK, now what would you like to do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I would like to get my-- to live with my sister again and hear are all her news.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, well, it will be very hard for her to get to here-- to get her here to England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know that hardly anybody can emigrate right now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I went home and didn't quite know what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I realized that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Roosevelt happened to be in London at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She stayed at the Dorchester Hotel, I think it was, in order to discuss the agenda for the forthcoming United Nations.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were planning it at least.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I wrote a letter to her explaining what happened to my sister-- if she could help me get my sister out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I really didn't expect an answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But within about three or four days, I had a long letter for-- from her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I still have it here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said that she feels with me very much and that I should see a certain Mrs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Robertson or Robinson.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it's in the letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That I should make an appointment with her, that maybe she can help get my sister out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I made this appointment with her and showed her Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Roosevelt's letter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after I showed her this letter, everything changed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- right away, she was on the phone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all this happened around March, I think, of 1946.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
